---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import LeafMark from '../components/LeafMark.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Garden & Art Landscapes"
  description="How Garden & Art Landscapes handles information submitted through this website."
>
  <main class="legal-page">
    <a class="thanks-brand" href="/" aria-label="Garden and Art Landscapes home">
      <LeafMark />
      <span>Garden <i>&</i> Art</span>
    </a>

    <article class="legal-content">
      <p class="eyebrow">Privacy policy</p>
      <h1>Simple, respectful<br /><em>communication.</em></h1>
      <p>When you submit the contact form, Garden & Art Landscapes receives the name, email address, phone number and project details you choose to provide.</p>
      <p>We use this information only to respond to your inquiry, discuss your project and provide requested services. We do not sell your personal information or add you to a marketing list without your permission.</p>
      <p>Form submissions are processed by the website hosting provider and may be retained for normal business follow-up and recordkeeping. To request access, correction or deletion of your information, email <a href="mailto:normanrabins@gmail.com">normanrabins@gmail.com</a>.</p>
      <a class="button button-clay" href="/">Return home</a>
    </article>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
